snippet.title: GoldenEye X - Singleplayer Preview Livestream
snippet.description:
Preview of the latest WIP version of GoldenEye X, including 9 playable singleplayer levels out of the original 20. Archives has a proof of concept 007 mode that includes bonus objectives, showcased at the end of the stream. As seen thorough the stream here you'll notice that the enemy accuracy and reaction time is broken on 00 Agent. This is a beta, and these will be polished on release.

Emulator tutorial: https://youtu.be/8mL0I__VMec
Download the emulator only from the official link - https://github.com/Graslu/1964GEPD/releases/tag/latest
